-- Travelers to Eliminate 450 Jobs This Week, Targeting Auto Unit
-- B y   M e g a n   H i c k e y
-- 2013-07-23T13:26:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-23/travelers-to-eliminate-450-jobs-this-week-targeting-auto-unit.html
Travelers Cos., the insurer cutting
jobs at its auto business, said it will give notice to about 450
employees this week that their positions are being eliminated.  The insurer will also cut jobs through attrition, Brian MacLean, the chief operating officer of New York-based Travelers
said today in a conference call.  To contact the reporter on this story:
